	* Sarayı sulayın: counter:hazine -10, counter:reaya 5
	* Gölgeye kaçın: counter:reaya -10, counter:kudret -5

Büyük Sel (card:afet_sel)
	bearer: character:sancakbeyi (variant:korkmus)
	weight: 0.2
	lockturn: 35
